{"tid":973711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬斯克接受中官媒訪問 稱對中國未來很樂觀","createTime":"2019-01-08T11:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T11:06:48.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a4d42ee0904e69fa69dcd507247022c001194e93","tid":973711,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"2019-01-08 16:39<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/01/08/phpCvyPPw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F01%2F08%2FphpCvyPPw.jpg&h=22531d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特斯拉（Tesla）上海車廠昨（7日）正式動工，馬斯克也親臨現場。（資料照，彭博）<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕特斯拉（Tesla）上海車廠昨（7日）正式動工，特斯拉CEO馬斯克（Elon Musk）也親臨現場。他接受中國官媒訪問時表示，他們對中國的未來很樂觀，認為中國在朝著正確的方向發展。<br />\n<br />\n根據《央視新聞》報導，馬斯克表示，中國的改革開放確實是有扎實的開放措施，長期來看他們對中國的未來很樂觀，認為中國在朝著正確的方向發展。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克表示，世界正朝著可持續交通、可持續能源的方向發展，直言中國在太陽能、電動車等領域是世界的領先者。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克表示，電動車市場龐大，而中國目前電動車在市場的佔比仍很小，所以對汽車企業來說機會巨大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/01/08/phpwt6jR6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F01%2F08%2Fphpwt6jR6.jpg&h=f8081115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬斯克在節目上表示對中國未來樂觀。（圖擷取自央視新聞）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2665412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2665412&d=Azaig5ye71GyeIzfdroQKMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=b1ea71d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2665412&h=bad7f1db\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2665412</a>"},{"pid":"addb3fd59f7b163126d81e96911c7660512ec9c6","tid":973711,"uid":100712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4d42ee0904e69fa69dcd507247022c001194e93","tid":973711,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit